{
  "message": "build: add src/ to test include path for internal header access\n\nAdd -I\\$(CURDIR)/src to TEST_CFLAGS so that test files can include\ninternal headers like runtime/runtime_internal.h. This is needed by\nthe new cleanup-stack integration tests in skeleton_test.c which\naccess asx_region_slot internals to push cleanup handlers directly.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
